data.thought: S20|P|S4|BRANCH D: Meta-notebooks. Highest novelty region. Core pattern: notebooks operating on notebooks. Self-reference, generation, optimization. Draws on: (1) Srcbook's .src.md format (serializable) (2) Thoughtbox's reasoning (meta-cognition) (3) Observatory's visualization (introspection). Key insight: if notebooks are code + reasoning, then meta-notebooks can reason about reasoning. Opens: self-improvement, notebook synthesis, reasoning optimization.
